SIMPLE: inauguration_day
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inauguration Day
<hw>In*au`gu*ra"tion Day</hw>. <def>The day on which the President of
the United States is inaugurated, the 20th of January in every year next
after a year divisible by four. Prior to the adoption of the twentieth
amendment to the Constitution of the United States (ratified February 6,
1933) the date was the 4th of March.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inaugurator</ent>⟦br⟧
